name: Kendall Jenner
description:
A request by @vincentshaw. Took me a while to get it done.

Similar to my Kim Kardashian model, most models already have an idea of how Kendall looks like, but an embedding provides consistency.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. There is a tendency for images to have her looking over her shoulder.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
